channel.title: Can't login to my own character
channel.description:
My server won't let me log into my own character. I am certain of the username and password, but it says the server must be down. And to make a new character. It lets me log in as other characters, but not my own.
This randomly happened for no reason..

item.title: Can't login to my own character
item.dc:creator: @inferno_vann inferno vann
item.description:
@inferno_vann wrote:

Yea, for a more detailed reason on how to fix this…

Go to character files, find yours, select all, copy it.

Delete your character file now.

Go into More Info, and delete that also.

Log in, Log out, Go to char files and find yours, paste, save, and you are done.

Hope I helped,
Inferno Vann
